<br>
Druids' and wizards' porting skills will still be invaluable for evac and just plain leaving a dungeon/raid. But if my comrades can get themselves to our place of battle in the first place it gives us all more time for the important things--like actually fighting and exploring.<br>
<br>
'Course, I've yet to charge for a port, so I don't exactly make that side of things a business.<br>
